### Create RxDB Database with Dexie Storage

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/rx-storage-dexie.html

Creates a new RxDB database instance using the Dexie storage adapter. This is a fundamental step for setting up a RxDB database with Dexie.

```javascript
const db = await createRxDatabase({
    name: 'exampledb',
    storage: getRxStorageDexie()
});
```

--------------------------------

### Import RxDB CouchDB Plugin and Dexie Storage

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/rx-storage-dexie.html

Imports necessary components from RxDB for CouchDB replication and Dexie storage. Ensures the required plugins are available for database creation and replication.

```javascript
import { replicateCouchDB } from 'rxdb/plugins/replication-couchdb';
import { getRxStorageDexie } from 'rxdb/plugins/storage-dexie';
import { createRxDatabase } from 'rxdb/plugins/core';
```

--------------------------------

### Import RxDB, Dexie Storage, and Dexie Cloud

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/rx-storage-dexie.html

Imports the necessary modules from RxDB core, the Dexie storage plugin, and the Dexie Cloud addon. This setup is required before creating a database with Dexie Cloud synchronization.

```javascript
import { createRxDatabase } from 'rxdb/plugins/core';
import { getRxStorageDexie } from 'rxdb/plugins/storage-dexie';
import dexieCloud from 'dexie-cloud-addon';
```

