### AsyncStorage Adapter Setup for RXDB (React Native)

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs-src/docs/adapters.md

This snippet shows how to configure RXDB to use AsyncStorage for data storage in React Native applications. It requires the 'pouchdb-adapter-asyncstorage' plugin. Note that this adapter has known issues and is not recommended for production use.

```javascript
// npm install pouchdb-adapter-asyncstorage --save
addPouchPlugin(require('pouchdb-adapter-asyncstorage'));

const database = await createRxDatabase({
    name: 'mydatabase',
    storage: getRxStoragePouch('node-asyncstorage') // the name of your adapter
});
```

