### RxDB IndexedDB (Reimplementation) Browser Storage Adapter

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/adapters.html

Demonstrates using a reimplemented IndexedDB adapter for RxDB, which utilizes native secondary indexes for potentially better performance. However, this adapter is not recommended due to reported issues and potential edge-case differences compared to the standard CouchDB/PouchDB implementation.

```javascript
// npm install pouchdb-adapter-indexeddb --save
addPouchPlugin(require('pouchdb-adapter-indexeddb'));

const database = await createRxDatabase({
    name: 'mydatabase',
    storage: getRxStoragePouch('indexeddb')
});
```

